# Classic GitHub personal access token, scope: read:user
# Used only at BUILD TIME (astro build) to fetch the public contribution
# calendar via GitHub's GraphQL API — never sent to the browser.
# Create one at https://github.com/settings/tokens
# Also add it as a repo secret (Settings > Secrets and variables > Actions)
# named GITHUB_CONTRIB_TOKEN so the CI build can fetch it too.
GITHUB_CONTRIB_TOKEN=
